EPL - Match of the Day 18.08.2018 720p HD
Video : MKV; H.264; 1280x720; 50 fps, ~5000 kbps
Audio : English (AAC, 2ch, 128 Kbps, 48 kHz)
Gary Lineker presents highlights from Saturday's Premier League matches. At Stamford Bridge Maurizio Sarri took charge of his first home game as Chelsea head coach, facing an Arsenal side with a new manager of their own in the guise of Unai Emery.

Elsewhere, newly promoted Fulham travelled to Tottenham and 2017-18 Championship winners Wolverhampton Wanderers visited Leicester City
